| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4870 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 41269da2-63e6-5317-8e19-aa46d88296c2"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
